title: Cycles and non randomness
description:
Various papers, presentations and a book on:

- Cycles, applied to markets, wars, human behavior, economics or accidents;
- non randomness, coming from cosmophysical influences as in the sun, moon and planets (Shnoll)

Includes Chizhevsky, Gorbanev, Armstrong, Marchetti, Payne, Edelson, Shnoll, Verma plus an additional (unrelated) article by Tesla.

Implications galore on the whole free will subject...
